---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Crystal Ridge KCK">
  <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl">Welcome to Crystal Ridge!</h2>
  <article
    class:list={[
      "container isolate grid gap-4 p-0 min-h-[350px] overflow-hidden bg-gray-50",
      "sm:grid-cols-[50%_auto]",
      "sm:shadow-none sm:overflow-visible",
    ]}
  >
    <img
      id="main-image"
      src="/front-entrance.jpeg"
      alt="front entrance"
      class:list={["inset-0 -z-10 h-full object-cover", "sm:rounded"]}
    />
    <div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 sm:rounded">
        <h3>Get Involved</h3>
        <p>
          <span class="w-8 inline-block"></span>
          We're dedicated to making our neighborhood the best it can be. Whether
          you're new to the area or have lived here for years, we want to make sure
          you're up-to-date on all the exciting changes happening in our community.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="w-8 inline-block"></span>
          We're working hard to get the clubhouse feeling like new, maintain our
          roads and common areas, and make our neighborhood a safe and enjoyable
          place to live. We believe that everyone can play a role in building a stronger
          community, and we would love to have you join us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  <a
    class="py-4 mt-8 mx-auto pb-0 w-fit ml-auto block"
    href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/319718186605123/"
    ><img src="/FindUs-FB-RGB.svg" class="h-8" alt="Find us on Facebook" /></a
  >
</Layout>
